videos.description: Ross Bowers sees the opening and rushes to the end zone, flying over Utah defense for a 9-yard touchdown in the 1st quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (QB keeps it, somersaults into the end zone for NIU) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: QB keeps it, somersaults into the end zone for NIU

videos.description: Demari Simpkins rushes 13 yards down the right side of the field to put Utah on the board vs. Northern Illinois.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah's Simpkins finds the open sideline for TD) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: Utah's Simpkins finds the open sideline for TD

videos.description: Tyler Huntley keeps the ball for himself and takes off running for the end zone, plowing his way through the defense for a 16-yard touchdown vs. Northern Illinois.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah QB takes off and bulldozes his way for TD) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: Utah QB takes off and bulldozes his way for TD

videos.description: Northern Illinois QB Ross Bowers sends a deep pass to Spencer Tears who jets to the end zone for a 74-yard TD to stay in contention with the Utah Utes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NIU converts 74-yard touchdown, hears boos from Utes fans) 2019/9/7

videos.headline: NIU converts 74-yard touchdown, hears boos from Utes fans

videos.description: Zack Moss first rushes through the pack for a 16-yard touchdown, then punches in another to pad Utah's lead over Northern Illinois.
